{"article_id":"1q2kkR5ufA5OJHWX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The comments from Lev Parnas , one of the men","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"who worked with Rudy Giuliani","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"to dig up dirt in Ukraine ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"come after Congress released hundreds of pages of evidence","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"that Parnas turned over to impeachment investigators .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"Lev Parnas , a key associate to Rudy Giuliani , a lawyer","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"working for President Donald Trump","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"who ran the Ukrainian backchannel campaign at the center of his impeachment ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"told MSNBC on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that `` President Trump knew exactly what was going on . ''","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"`` He was aware of all my movements .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"I would n't do anything","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"without the consent of Rudy Giuliani or the president , ''","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Parnas ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"who was indicted on campaign finance charges ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"told MSNBC host Rachel Maddow .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"`` Why would [ Ukrainian ] President Zelenskiy 's inner circle or Minister Avakov or all these people or President Poroshenko meet with me ?","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Who am I ?","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"They were told to meet with me .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"And that 's the secret","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that they 're trying to keep .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"I was on the ground","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"doing their work . ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The interview aired","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"after House Democrats released hundreds of pages of new documents","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"related to the impeachment inquiry into President Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"including texts and notes","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"turned over by Parnas .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Three House committees sent the evidence to the House Judiciary Committee on Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" to be included as part of the official record","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"that will be transmitted to the Senate along with the Articles of Impeachment. \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The House sent the articles to the Senate on Wednesday evening .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"In a statement to MSNBC","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"as the interview aired ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Giuliani said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Parnas had `` never '' spoken on behalf of Trump in his meetings .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that Parnas is `` a very sad situation . ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The evidence","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"sent by the Intelligence , Oversight , and Foreign Affairs committees","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"included documents","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"provided recently by Parnas ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"who helped Giuliani dig up dirt on former Vice President Joe Biden , in response to a subpoena","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"he received from the House in October .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"The committees said","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"the evidence also included call records ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"which they did not make public due to their sensitivity .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"\" All of this new evidence confirms what we already know :","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"the President and his associates pressured Ukrainian officials to announce investigations","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that would benefit the President politically , \"","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"the chairs of all four committees said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The committees said","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Parnas \" continues to provide material responsive to the subpoena on a rolling basis. \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Here are some highlights from the documents","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"the committees made public :","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Parnas ' s handwritten notes show","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"plans","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"to get the Ukrainians to investigate Joe Biden","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"House Intelligence Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"House Intelligence Committee","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"/ Via intelligence.house.gov","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"The notes ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"written on stationery from the Ritz-Carlton hotel in Vienna","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"appear to be a to-do list","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"related to Parnas ' s efforts","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to find incriminating information on Biden , one of the president ' s top Democratic rivals .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"The former vice president ' s son Hunter worked for a Ukrainian gas company","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that faced corruption allegations .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Parnas may have written the notes last July ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"as he notes in texts to Giuliani on July 2","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that he was headed to Vienna .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"\" [ T ] rying to get us mr Z , \"","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Parnas told Giuliani at the time ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"appearing to reference a meeting with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"One bullet in the notes reads ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"\" get Zalensky to Annonce","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"that the Biden case will Be Investigated. \"","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"In another , Parnas says","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"to \" start commun [ icating ] with \" Zelensky","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"without involving two Ukrainian oligarchs","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"- Victor Pinchuk and Igor Kolomoisky .","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"Parnas and his business partner Igor Fruman previously sought to use Kolomoisky","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"to set up a meeting with Zelensky .","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"\" Put together a package , \"","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"reads the next point ,","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"and \" go to DC with package. \"","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"The following bullet says","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"Parnas should do his \" magic \"","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"and \" cut deal. \"","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"( Deal is underlined twice . )","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Two Trumpworld lawyers","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"- Victoria Toensing and Joe diGenova -","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"are mentioned as having been \" retained \" at $ 100,000 per month .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"The notes also say","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to hire one of two well-connected lobbyists in Trump ' s Washington :","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Brian Ballard and Robert Stryk .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Parnas cashed two checks","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"totaling $ 45,000","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"from Ballard ' s firm in 2018 for work","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"it has said","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"is unrelated to Ukraine .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Giuliani tells the Ukrainian president","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"he has Trump ' s \" knowledge and consent \"","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"to seek a meeting","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"House Intelligence Committee","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"/ Via intelligence.house.gov","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"In a letter","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"dated May 10 , 2019 ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Giuliani introduced himself to Zelensky as Trump ' s personal lawyer","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"and congratulated Zelensky on his \" truly impressive victory \" in the Ukrainian presidential election .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"\" Along with many others , I am very hopeful","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that your election is a real turning point","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"and allows the Ukraine to prosper","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and overcome some or the long-standing problems of the past , \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Giuliani wrote .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"\" Anything","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"I can do","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"to help you or your country","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"would be a great honor .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"\" However , I have a more specific request , \"","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"he continued .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"\" In my capacity as personal counsel to President Trump and with his knowledge and consent , I request a meeting with you on this upcoming Monday , May 13th or Tuesday , May 14th .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"I will need no more than a half-hour of your time","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"and I will be accompanied by my colleague Victoria Toensing , a distinguished American attorney","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"who is very familiar with this matter. \"","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Trump would speak with Zelensky by phone two months later","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"after placing a hold on millions in foreign aid to Ukraine .","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"Trump has sought to distance himself from Giuliani ' s efforts","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"to find incriminating evidence on Biden in Ukraine .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Trump \" consents \" to having his former lawyer represent Parnas","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"House Intelligence Committee / Via intelligence.house.gov","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Parnas and Fruman were originally represented in the impeachment inquiry by John Dowd ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"who once served as the president ' s lead lawyer in former special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"\" I have discussed the issue of representation with the President , \"","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Jay Sekulow , the president ' s current lawyer , wrote to Dowd on Oct. 2 .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"\" The President consents to allowing your representation of Mr. Parnas and Mr. Furman. \"","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Parnas and Fruman were later arrested on campaign finance charges","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"as they prepared to leave the country ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"and both have new lawyers","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"representing them in the criminal investigation .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Texts to Parnas suggest","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"the US ambassador to Ukraine","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"- whom Trump removed -","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"was being closely monitored in Kyiv","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"House Intelligence Committee / Via intelligence.house.gov , House Intelligence Committee / Via intelligence.house.gov","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Text messages","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"turned over by Parnas","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"show his efforts","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"to have then-US ambassador Marie Yovanovitch","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"- a prominent anti-corruption advocate -","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"recalled from her post in Ukraine .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"Parnas was working with Yuriy Lutsenko , the former prosecutor general of Ukraine ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"to dig up dirt on the Bidens -","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"and text messages between the pair reveal","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"why removing the ambassador was important to them .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"\" It ' s just that","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"if you don ' t make a decision about Madam-you are bringing into question all my allegations .","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"Including about B , \"","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"Lutsenko told Parnas last March ,","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"according to a translation by the Intelligence Committee .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"Texts between Parnas and Robert F. Hyde , a Republican","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"who ' s running for Congress in Connecticut this year ,","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"suggest","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"Yovanovitch was under surveillance in Kyiv","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"before she was abruptly recalled to Washington .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"Yovanovitch had previously said","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"she was told by a Trump administration officials","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"that her recall was related to her \" security , \"","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"but that it was unclear what that meant .","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"\" Can ' t believe","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"Trumo hasn ' t fired this bitch .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"I ' ll get right in that , \"","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"Hyde texted Parnas in March 2019 ,","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"after Parnashe sent him press coverage about Yovanovitch .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"\" She under heavy protection outside Kiev , \"","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Hyde wrote later that day .","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"\" I know crazy shit , \"","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"Parnas responded .","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"\" My guy thinks","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"maybe FSB .. ? \"","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"Hyde said ,","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"apparently referring to the Russian spy agency .","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"The men continued messaging each other on WhatsApp .","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"Two days later , Hyde sent Parnas a series of texts about Yovanovitch ' s supposed movements .","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"\" The guys over they asked me what I would like to do","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"and what is in it for them , \"","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"Hyde said .","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"\" They will let me know","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"when she ' s on the move , \"","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"he later said .","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"\" Perfect , \"","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Parnas replied .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"\" They are willing to help","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"if we/you would like a price .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"Guess you can do anything in the Ukraine with money ...","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"what I was told , \"","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"Hyde said .","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"\" Lol , \"","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"Parnas responded .","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"In a statement Tuesday night , an attorney for Yovanovitch called the idea","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"that she was being surveilled","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"`` disturbing ''","depth":7},{"id":204,"text":"and called for an investigation by the `` appropriate authorities . ''","depth":6},{"id":205,"text":"Hyde ' s campaign did not immediately return ' requests for comment","depth":6},{"id":206,"text":"but on Twitter said","depth":8},{"id":207,"text":"he was `` never in Kiev ''","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"and called House Intelligence Committee chairman Adam Schiff a `` turd . ''","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"How low can liddle Adam Bull Schiff go ?","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"I was never in Kiev .","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"For them to take some texts","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"my buddy ' s and I wrote back to some dweeb","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"we were playing with","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"that we met a few times","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"while we had a few drinks","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"is definitely laughable .","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"Schiff is a desperate turd","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"playing with this Lev guy .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":437,"left":223,"right":436,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":221,"right":222,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":1,